OL,3,CWater companies ask to hike bills by
OL,4,Cmore than first planned
OL,6,FThis summer, the regulator pared back
OL,7,Fthose requests to an average of #535,
OL,8,Fin its draft price review in July.
OL,10,FNow, after a consultation period, 10
OL,11,Fof the 11 water companies have hit
OL,12,Fback with higher requests than before.
OL,14,FThe biggest proposed rise is by
OL,15,FSouthern Water, which would see bills
OL,16,Ffor its customers in Sussex, Kent and
OL,17,FHampshire rise by 84% between now and
OL,18,F2030.
