OL,3,CWater companies ask to hike bills by
OL,4,Cmore than first planned
OL,6,FThames Water, the UK's biggest
OL,7,Fprovider, which is in emergency talks
OL,8,Fover a #15 billion debt pile and a
OL,9,Fworsening financial situation, has
OL,10,Fasked for a 53% rise.
OL,12,FMany water companies argue they need
OL,13,Fto spend more on upgrading their
OL,14,Fpipes, sewers and reservoirs than
OL,15,Foriginally planned, and therefore need
OL,16,Fbills to go up too.
