OL,3,CWater companies ask to hike bills by
OL,4,Cmore than first planned
OL,6,FOfwat wrote in an update on Tuesday
OL,7,Fthat this was "mostly to meet the
OL,8,Frequirements of other regulators like
OL,9,Fthe Environment Agency and Drinking
OL,10,FWater Inspectorate".
OL,12,FBut some of the increases are designed
OL,13,Fto meet "changes to the proposed rate
OL,14,Fof return for investors".
OL,16,FOfwat is due to make a final decision
OL,17,Fon bills increases on December 19,
OL,18,Fwith companies going to the
OL,19,Fnegotiating table with regulators
OL,20,Fbefore then.
