OL,3,CWater companies ask to hike bills by
OL,4,Cmore than first planned
OL,6,FThe regulator wrote: "We will consider
OL,7,Fthis additional expenditure request as
OL,8,Fpart of our final determinations".
OL,10,FThe latest string of demands come amid
OL,11,Fpublic and political outcry over
OL,12,Fsewage spills in the privatised water
OL,13,Findustry.
OL,15,FA recent performance report by Ofwat
OL,16,Fshowed there has only been a 2%
OL,17,Freduction in pollution since 2019
OL,18,Fdespite firms committing to cutting it
OL,19,Fby 30%.
