OL,3,CWater companies ask to hike bills by
OL,4,Cmore than first planned
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,7,Fspokesman said: "Clearly no one wanted
OL,8,Fto see a situation where water bills
OL,9,Fare rising, where the water sector has
OL,10,Fgot into the situation that it has
OL,11,Fwith record levels of sewage spills
OL,12,Fand ageing infrastructure.
OL,14,F"That's why when this Government came
OL,15,Fin they set out a raft of measures to
OL,16,Fdrive change in the industry, clean up
OL,17,Four waterways, including the new Water
OL,18,FBill."
