OL,6,FHe added: "Ofwat are the independent
OL,7,Fregulator and will make their final
OL,8,Fdetermination in December.
OL,10,F"From the Government's perspective,
OL,11,Four priority is making sure that money
OL,12,Fgoes where it's needed and ensuring
OL,13,Fthat water companies are putting
OL,14,Fcustomers first. If money isn't spent,
OL,15,Fit will be returned to customers."
